<l>paṉiyarumpip paitalkoṇ mālai tuṉiyarumpit </l>
<l> tuṉpam vaḷara varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The evening that (once) came in with trembling and dimness (now) brings me an aversion for life and increasing sorrow.</l>
